{"tid":1331682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［新手開post］721會留低打機既社工朋友入黎俾兩句意見","createTime":"2019-07-19T04:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T04:44:14.000Z","uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dcbc261f510a9424d5103a93c5d64e6116b074cb","tid":1331682,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"我係個支持勇武既和理非<br />\n721打機果日前排既義士同警察唔知會發生咩衝突<br />\n但係咩衝突都好 我都好想用和理非既方式去幫同保護前排義士既徹退<br />\n之前發夢見到有社工幫手拖住警察清場，等義士可以有時間撤離  而我亦都想做類似既事情<br />\n但我係個未grad社工系學生 未有社工證 亦都無上前排既經驗 所以唔知呢個方式點樣 想問下各位專業既社工朋友既意見，因為我真係好唔想前排義士再被人捉"},{"pid":"7f9a2a9217e2eda09c66362fc87baa67aaecf89d","tid":1331682,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGem6Rf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGem6Rf.png&h=b24b8c13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5pY84L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5pY84L.png&h=3ded51ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mijY84T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmijY84T.png&h=82615ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}